Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 稍事休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…小玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木的父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:20.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}玛雅的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我一口气把天花板摔到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在天花板的里面密密麻麻地贴着几百个护符
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一大堆事情要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚准备要说高潮部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窥伺房间的红脸的真正面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡得真爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在炎热的日子吃西瓜 这才是夏天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 关于小玛雅的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还是别来无恙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那样啊 那就肯定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在应该在孤独地吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好给力！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸亲手制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看这样 还是很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲星期天还照常开工？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那噪音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 玛雅小学的时候是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然扯到我头上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到久未到访的朋友家里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回味过去的事情不是惯例吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好东西哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读了这些作文之后 你就知道玛雅小时候是怎样的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 梢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我将来的梦想 3年1班 神代玛雅」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我将来的梦想是 去那个叫英国的地方 到尼斯湖捉尼斯湖水怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很强大啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅小时候就很喜欢超自然现象的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那时无知而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即时再没判断力的小朋友 也是会成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是觉得你5年级时的文集也很强大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…曾被外星人带到泽塔双星上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}泽塔双星(Zeta Reticuli)：由泽塔1号和泽塔2号组成的联星系统，两星\n绕其共同质量中心旋转一圈需要100万年。曾于《异形》等多套科幻作品中出现。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再读了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.06,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊梢啊 看这里 这是玛雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们玩得很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你能吃这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么定食屋会有布丁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你才是 怎么一直都吃同样的的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢布丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 例牌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是送的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没吃够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们两个的关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天黑夜都在一起出没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要一起打工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.24,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}谜之怪圈出现！！  外星人的信息？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一条新闻是 在長野市松代县发现的谜之怪圈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋 太恶心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手啊停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之怪圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昨晚之前 未有发现任何异常状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 这有可能是某些组织在昨晚到今晨制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,县内警方正调查是否恶意捣乱的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 快看 真正的谜之怪圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛那么认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻都说了那是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我想起有点急事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得赶紧走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 肯定有问题就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等下在现场见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车吧 小玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去看谜之怪圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐还是不坐啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谜之怪圈就是正宗的超自然现象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那个 坐在货车的货舱上没有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说那个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之怪圈在等着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 给点力 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人山人海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不到心灰意冷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这个的UFO或者外星人有可能是钥匙 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪圈是在昨晚到今天凌晨之间出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有UFO出现的话 也就是那个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚开始就在这埋伏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 我在想你今天还真是很尽心地帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩为啥还在这转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老师让我们给他带路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了 我还有些事情要你们来做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我找你们之前随便打发一下时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我干活去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今晚 在这里集合可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 时间的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十点如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要回去吃晚饭对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后可以吃西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问要一起去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有趣的事情 只有你们两个人享受也太狡猾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要保护者同行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞开肚皮吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:01.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢吃肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:02.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我也要过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.92,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}玉屋和键屋：江户时代烟花师傅的代表人物的称号，二者齐名，后成烟花的代名词。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,键屋～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 拿点气势出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 时间到了再叫醒他们就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 没想到玛雅对谜之怪圈会有那么大的反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说就算发生了那么多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玛雅还是那个小玛雅 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了玛雅做了这么多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么暗的环境 能拍下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就相信未来的科技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么未来的科技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这上面还有灯 专门来对付这种情况的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 是哪个按钮来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出 出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你也赶紧拍照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候跑那么远去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点上来 不然就跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废啊你 对着天空拍照干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晃 很难拍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 把速度降一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 右边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飙起来飙起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这种时间 也不会有其他车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚 亚 亚 亚美同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了我不认识的亚美同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦 老爸的操纵技术是日本第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飙起来吧 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边左转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向学校那边飞去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 这回是货真价实的诺查丹玛斯之钥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Father牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来是牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太胆小了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是都市里长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来全身的血液都抽干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠牛事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.38,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}屠牛事件（Cattle mutilation）：最早出现于美国，指牛（或其他牲畜）身上的某些部位\n被非常精确规则地切下，体内的血液也被抽干。普遍怀疑是外星人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}电池电力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道也是外星人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 有什么东西出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灰人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.66,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小灰人（Greys）：又称为罗斯威尔外星人或者Zetas，也作外星生命的统称。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那跟我所知道的外星人不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都好 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记脑子里要想着破坏它了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JK？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴 暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑木她爸爸拜托你们的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之怪圈也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 全部都是骗局了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 你为什么骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想再看看小玛雅开怀大笑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个全裸穿着草鞋的老女人从电线杆的阴影里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你现在讨厌超自然现象了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你老爸突然过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上不习惯的校长工作 你一定很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个小玛雅不是那么容易改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在勉强着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 就算这样也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这样做很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个大人 你不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种 这种小孩子的恶作剧 才没有时间奉陪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你践踏老爸的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么讨厌的话 就一辈子讨厌好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对超自然也是 对老爸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我向小玛雅道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊 亚美同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为那个是钥匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有点这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着或许我们能改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是为了我自己而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要我来做下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做啊 你不是主角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别狡辩了快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会原谅说老爸坏话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦 你们两位 吃点这个和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末超自然学院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 不变的亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:07.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}取意大利语mamamia（我的天呀）的谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副标题已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------OP----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:05.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}十年先の未来が 見える魔法をがあったらな...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:15.49,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}追いかけ続ける程 逃げてく世界の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:20.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}悩まずいられるのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:25.10,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}時を切り裂くような速さで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}駆け抜けてく　流されてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}空に揺らねながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:43.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕らは飛び立とうとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.84,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さんざん見た未来地図と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:54.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}折れた翼広げ 広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:59.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今 始まろとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰か呼ぶ声がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:14.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}暁を染めて　染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:05.01,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要是有魔法能预见十年后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:15.49,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在这越是追寻 却离得越远的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:20.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}本应充满烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:25.10,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以仿若切开时间般的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}飞奔而去 顺流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使只能在空中摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:43.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我们正欲起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.84,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}展开早已熟读的未来地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:54.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}和那折断的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:59.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}现在 一切就要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}耳中传来谁人的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:14.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}将那片晨光染尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------ED----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君だけのため　光る世界　ここにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}幼い手で握りしめてた　失くさないよ　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}真っ白な願いを　君と追いかけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}まだ迷い込む　寂しいげな夜だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}あの日の面影を　見つけで　思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がいるから　どこでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}何度、転んでも　笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然だとか　必然だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要らないほど　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:25.12,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと輝く　思い出なら　君の側にだけ　あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:33.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大切な世界　離さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仅属于你的光辉世界 就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握着你幼小的手 牢牢地不让它溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}纯白的心愿 与你共同追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若是被踌躇包围 寂寞如水的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}请于记忆深处 再次寻回 那天的音容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为有你在旁 不管身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.92,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使不断跌倒 也会笑着面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是偶然 还是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我已变得无比坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:25.12,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若能缔造闪耀回忆 必因有你在旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:33.54,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最珍贵的世界 两手紧握 不再松开
